    """Create a routine that takes a collection of textual items.
    The collection contains distinct entries. Return the entry with the greatest
    amount of varied characters. If several entries share the greatest amount
    of varied characters, return the one that would appear earlier under a
    common textual ordering.

    pick_one(["name", "of", "string"]) == "string"
    pick_one(["name", "enam", "game"]) == "enam"
    pick_one(["aaaaaaa", "bb" ,"cc"]) == ""aaaaaaa"
